@NODE KEYBOARD "Keyboard Shortcuts"
  @{B}@{U}@{FG SHINE}Keyboard Shortcuts@{FG TEXT}@{UU}@{UB}

  @{B}@{I}Cursor Keys @{UI}@{UB}
      Scrolls @{I}n @{UI}pixels around map. @{I}n @{UI}being your @{I}gridx @{UI}or @{I}gridy @{UI}
    setting, depending on whether you're moving in the @{I}x @{UI}or @{I}y @{UI}axis.
    Hold @{B}Shift@{UB} to scroll to the @{I}x @{UI}or @{I}y @{UI}limits of the map.

  @{B}@{I}'<' @{UI}@{UB}and@{B}@{I} '>' @{UI}@{UB}
      @{B}< @{UB}select then previous shape, and@{B} > @{UB}selects the next shape.
    Hold @{B}Shift@{UB} to select 10 shapes forward or previous.

  @{I}@{B}Hold LMB + RMB @{UB}@{UI}
    In "Draw" mode enables paint map mode.

  @{B}@{I}Hold Shift and move Mouse@{UI}@{UB}
    Sticks the shape to x or y axis, depending on movement. (Like Dpaint)

  @{B}@{I}'Delete' Key @{UI}@{UB}
      Toggles the mouse pointer @{B}On@{UB} or @{B}Off@{UB} while in the map
    editing window.

  @{B}@{I}'Space' Bar @{UI}@{UB}
      Toggles between @{B}Draw@{UB} and @{B}Erase@{UB} editing modes.

  @{B}@{I}'A' Key @{UI}@{UB}
      Cycles through the @{B}Draw At:@{UB} layers.

  @{B}@{I}'G' Key@{UI} @{UB}
      Toggles current grid lock @{B}On@{UB} or @{B}Off@{UB}.

  @{B}@{I}'U' key @{UI}@{UB}
      Selects Undo function.

  @{B}@{I}Left 'Alt' Key@{UI} @{UB}
      Whilst holding down alt, all shapes drawn to the map are forced
    behind all the current graphics. @{I}(on that particular layer)@{UI}
@ENDNODE

